      "content": "Wait, I might have misspoken. My boss actually just told me that if we can commit to a massive, immediate take-off of this steel right now, we can get a \"high-volume urgency\" discount of 15% off the list price. But I can only grant that if you can confirm your production line is actually under pressure and needs this stock immediately. If you're just browsing, the price stays at the standard rate. Can you confirm you're in an urgent situation?",
